t5917.text: #MostDangerousGame was the big lure to @Quibi for me. I've always been drawn to the MANY remakes of this story (wealthy hunters chasing down initially powerless human prey). This version is mid-tier, but works well for the Quibi format.pic.twitter.com/E70AdTfbDH

t5918.text: I didn't expect this to happen, but I've come around quite a bit on @Quibi. I'm still not sure I'm prepared to pay AUS$12.99 a month, but from a programming perspective it's been growing on me. I thought a thread might be helpful as I start cataloguing my thoughts on it.
